From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000009 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Petr Parkan Janda <petr.parkan.janda@oh-so.com>
Date: Sun, 22 Jun 2026 18:30:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] ARM: OMAP4: steelhead: SEV in prepare_cpus to wake CPU1 (stock parity)

On the OMAP4460 HS Nexus Q, CONFIG_SMP silently deadlocked the whole boot
(no console/HDMI/network) when CPU1 was brought up. Disassembling the stock
Android 3.0.8 SMP kernel (reverse-eng/vmlinux.bin) shows stock issues an SEV
inside platform_smp_prepare_cpus (dmb;dsb;sev;dsb) immediately after writing
the CPU1 startup address to AUX_CORE_BOOT_1. Out of cold U-Boot reset CPU1 is
parked in ROM WFE; the ROM only (re)reads AUX_CORE_BOOT_1 after an SEV wakes it,
moving CPU1 into the kernel secondary hold loop. Mainline omap4_smp_prepare_cpus
omits this SEV and relies solely on the later SGI + dsb_sev in
omap4_boot_secondary, so on this bootloader CPU1 never leaves ROM WFE and
__cpu_up() blocks during smp_init, before any console -> the silent hang.

Mirror stock: add dsb_sev() at the end of omap4_smp_prepare_cpus, after the
AUX_CORE_BOOT_1 write. Verified on hardware: CPU1 comes online (nproc=2).

Note: pair with cpuidle.off=1 on the cmdline (stock ships
cpuidle44xx.disallow_smp_idle) -- OMAP4 secondary deep-idle otherwise faults.

Signed-off-by: Petr Parkan Janda <petr.parkan.janda@oh-so.com>
---
--- a/arch/arm/mach-omap2/omap-smp.c
+++ b/arch/arm/mach-omap2/omap-smp.c
@@ -403,6 +403,16 @@
 	else
 		writel_relaxed(__pa_symbol(cfg.startup_addr),
 			       cfg.wakeupgen_base + OMAP_AUX_CORE_BOOT_1);
+
+	/*
+	 * Steelhead OMAP4460 HS: stock issues an SEV here, in prepare, right after
+	 * writing AUX_CORE_BOOT_1, to kick CPU1 out of ROM WFE so it reads the
+	 * startup address and enters the kernel secondary hold loop. Mainline omits
+	 * this and relies only on the later SGI + dsb_sev in omap4_boot_secondary,
+	 * which on a cold U-Boot boot leaves CPU1 parked in ROM WFE -> the OMAP4
+	 * silent SMP deadlock. Mirror stock (vmlinux.bin platform_smp_prepare_cpus).
+	 */
+	dsb_sev();
 }
 
 const struct smp_operations omap4_smp_ops __initconst = {
